$ %VCToolsInstallDir%

Subdirectories:
  • atlmfc
  • → Windows/dirs/Program-Files-x86/Microsoft-Visual-Studio/version/edition/VC/Tools/MSVC/version/bin[bin]
  • crt, below which is → Windows/dirs/Program-Files-x86/Microsoft-Visual-Studio/version/edition/VC/Tools/MSVC/version/crt/src/vcruntime[src/vcruntime], the source of the VC specific parts of the CRT.
  • → Windows/dirs/Program-Files-x86/Microsoft-Visual-Studio/version/edition/VC/Tools/MSVC/version/include[include]
  • → Windows/dirs/Program-Files-x86/Microsoft-Visual-Studio/version/edition/VC/Tools/MSVC/version/lib[lib]
  • vcperf

The version number that is included in `%VCToolsInstallDir%` can be found in a file like
→ Windows/dirs/Program-Files-x86/Microsoft-Visual-Studio/version/edition/VC/Auxiliary/Build/Microsoft_VCToolsVersion_default_txt[`C:\Program Files (x86)\Microsoft Visual Studio\2019\Community\VC\Auxiliary\Build\Microsoft.VCToolsVersion.default.txt`].
